
make clean: clean all boards bootloaders. Keep built U-boot bins (boot block binaries in main/lib/u-boot/* are NOT deleted)

make clean-all: cleans ALL boards bootloaders and also boards built u-boot binaries in main/lib/u-boot/*

make clean-bootloader: the same like clean

When you change board, you need clean image from previous board.
For refresh bootloader after changing board run:
1. make bootloaders/clean
2. set new board in minimyth.conf
3. make bootloaders/install